{"text_koine":"Θησεὺς ἐν οἴκῳ ἐστίν. θέλει φαγεῖν ἄρτον· πορεύεται πρὸς τὴν ἀγοράν.","text_english":"Theseus is in the house. He wants to eat bread; he goes to the market.","art_instructions":"Interior of a simple home; Theseus ready to go, thinking of bread (small bread icon/thought).","art_characters":"Theseus the Owl"}
{"text_koine":"ἔρχεται ἔξω πρὸς τὴν ὁδόν. ἐνταῦθα τέσσαρες ὁδοί εἰσιν.","text_english":"He comes out to the road. Here there are four roads.","art_instructions":"A four-way crossroads: mountain path, forest path, cave path, and a sunny open road toward a small agora.","art_characters":"Theseus the Owl"}
{"text_koine":"Θησεὺς εἰς τὸ ὄρος πορεύεται.","text_english":"Theseus goes into the mountain.","art_instructions":"Theseus enters a mountain path; rocky slopes ahead.","art_characters":"Theseus the Owl"}
{"text_koine":"ἡ Σφίγξ ἐν τῷ ὄρει ἐστίν. δεινή ἐστιν.","text_english":"The Sphinx is in the mountain. She is fierce.","art_instructions":"Friendly depiction of a Sphinx silhouette blocking the mountain path (non-scary).","art_characters":"Theseus the Owl, Sphinx"}
{"text_koine":"Θησεὺς λέγει· οὐδαμῶς. ἐκ τοῦ ὄρους ἐξέρχεται. πορεύεται ἄλλην ὁδόν.","text_english":"Theseus says, 'No way.' He goes out of the mountain. He goes another road.","art_instructions":"Theseus turns around on the mountain path and returns toward the crossroads.","art_characters":"Theseus the Owl"}
{"text_koine":"Θησεὺς εἰς τὸ δάσος πορεύεται.","text_english":"Theseus goes into the forest.","art_instructions":"Theseus enters a leafy forest path.","art_characters":"Theseus the Owl"}
{"text_koine":"ὁ Κύκλωψ ἐν τῷ δάσει ἐστίν. δεινός ἐστιν.","text_english":"The Cyclops is in the forest. He is fierce.","art_instructions":"Large Cyclops silhouette among trees, clearly blocking the way (non-scary).","art_characters":"Theseus the Owl, Cyclops"}
{"text_koine":"Θησεὺς λέγει· οὐδαμῶς. ἐκ τοῦ δάσους ἐξέρχεται. πορεύεται ἄλλην ὁδόν.","text_english":"Theseus says, 'No way.' He goes out of the forest. He goes another road.","art_instructions":"Theseus calmly exits the forest path back toward the crossroads.","art_characters":"Theseus the Owl"}
{"text_koine":"Θησεὺς εἰς τὸ σπήλαιον πορεύεται.","text_english":"Theseus goes into the cave.","art_instructions":"Theseus approaches and steps into a cave mouth path.","art_characters":"Theseus the Owl"}
{"text_koine":"ὁ Κέρβερος ἐν τῷ σπηλαίῳ ἐστίν. δεινός ἐστιν.","text_english":"Cerberus is in the cave. He is fierce.","art_instructions":"Three‑headed dog silhouette blocking the cave path (gentle, not gory).","art_characters":"Theseus the Owl, Cerberus"}
{"text_koine":"Θησεὺς λέγει· οὐδαμῶς. ἐκ τοῦ σπηλαίου ἐξέρχεται. πορεύεται ἄλλην ὁδόν.","text_english":"Theseus says, 'No way.' He goes out of the cave. He goes another road.","art_instructions":"Theseus exits the cave path and heads back toward the crossroads.","art_characters":"Theseus the Owl"}
{"text_koine":"Θησεὺς βλέπει ἀγαθὴν ὁδόν καὶ ἥλιον. τέρατα οὐκ ἔστιν ἐκεῖ.","text_english":"Theseus sees a good road and sun. There are no monsters there.","art_instructions":"Sunlit, open path leading toward a small agora; the other paths faintly behind.","art_characters":"Theseus the Owl"}
{"text_koine":"Θησεὺς περιπατεῖ ἠρέμα· εἶτα τρέχει ταχέως.","text_english":"Theseus walks gently; then he runs quickly.","art_instructions":"Two-action scene of Theseus first walking, then running along the clear road.","art_characters":"Theseus the Owl"}
{"text_koine":"ἔρχεται εἰς τὴν ἀγοράν. τράπεζα ἐνταῦθα· ἄρτος καὶ ὕδωρ.","text_english":"He comes into the market. A table is here: bread and water.","art_instructions":"Simple agora stall with bread and water on a table; Theseus arrives happily.","art_characters":"Theseus the Owl"}
{"text_koine":"Θησεὺς λαμβάνει ἄρτον. ἐσθίει ἄρτον καὶ πίνει ὕδωρ.","text_english":"Theseus takes bread. He eats bread and drinks water.","art_instructions":"Theseus nibbling bread and sipping water at the market.","art_characters":"Theseus the Owl"}
{"text_koine":"Θησεὺς λέγει· εὐχαριστῶ.","text_english":"Theseus says, 'Thank you.'","art_instructions":"Theseus smiles and gives a small thankful gesture in the agora.","art_characters":"Theseus the Owl"}
